1598068800.title: CNN Newsroom
1598068800.descr: CNN Newroom provides the most up to date news as it breaks and is the longest running show on the channel, airing twice a day Monday to Friday and throughout the day over the weekends. CNN was founding in 1980 by American media proprietor Ted Turner as a 24 hour cable news channel and has since won multiple media awards.

1598069700.title: Marketplace Africa
1598069700.descr: Marketplace Africa on CNN offers unique access to the latest African market information, with a look at events and developments that impact its business world. Eleni Giokos is the show's host. Every week she interviews figures of business and industry to reveal the economic trends in various regions of Africa and to present the continent's key sectors and corporations.

1598070600.title: Inside Africa
1598070600.descr: Each week, Inside Africa documentary series on CNN highlights the unique diversity of mysterious Africa, its numerous cultures and religions, peoples, art, music, cuisine, travel and literature, its one-of-a-kind flora and fauna. Everything what Africa is filled with and lives for is in this series.

1598072400.title: Quest's World of Wonder
1598072400.descr: Join our host, Richard Quest, as he takes us on a journey of discovery to some of the most iconic cities on the planet. Richard encounters many of the influential local inhabitants and delves into the heritage and culture of each city to reveal what makes them unique and fascinating. The first series sees Richard travel around the globe to visit Washington D.C., Panama City, Nairobi, London, Berlin and Istanbul.
